# Commit message format:
# type(scope): short description (imperative mood, ≤72 chars)
#
# Types: feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, test, chore, ci, perf, build
# Scope: affected layer/component (optional but preferred)
#
# Examples:
# feat(api): add user authentication endpoint
# fix(core): resolve database connection timeout
# docs(readme): update installation instructions
#
# No Co-Authored-By trailers. No trailing periods on subject line.